commit.message:
tm.texi (FUNCTION_ARG): Document that @var{type} can be an incomplete type.

2001-01-02  Jeffrey Oldham  <oldham@codesourcery.com>

	* tm.texi (FUNCTION_ARG): Document that @var{type} can be an
	incomplete type.

From-SVN: r38626
